---
title: African-Inspired Chicken and Peanut Soup with Kidney Beans and Sesame Flatbreads
description: Rich peanut butter and fibre-loaded kidney beans make for a creamy and oh-so-filling soup. The golden sesame seed flatbreads are perfect for dipping. You'll want to make this one when you feel like loading up on veggies.
